    note right of TNotExplicitCNotExplicit
        Tiling mode: DEFAULT, DISABLED, or COPY_FROM_METADATA.
        Compression mode: DEFAULT, DISABLED, or COPY_FROM_METADATA.
        setTiling(), getTileWidth/Height/Offset(), setCompressionType(),
        getCompressionType(), setCompressionQuality(), etc. are all forbidden.
    end note

    note right of TExplicitCExplicit
        Tiling mode: MODE_EXPLICIT, but setTiling() not yet called.
        Compression mode: MODE_EXPLICIT, but no compression type set yet.
        getTileWidth/Height/Offset() and getLocalizedCompressionTypeName(),
        setCompressionQuality() (if types exist) are forbidden.
    end note

    note right of TExplicitSetCExplicitTyped
        Tiling: MODE_EXPLICIT and setTiling() called.
        Compression: MODE_EXPLICIT and compression type set.
        All tiling and compression methods available.
    end note

    note right of TExplicitCNotExplicit
        setTilingMode(MODE_EXPLICIT) moves to TExplicit states.
        setTilingMode(non-EXPLICIT) moves to TNotExplicit states.
        Value-sensitive parameter: mode determines target state.
    end note

    note right of TNotExplicitCExplicit
        setCompressionMode(MODE_EXPLICIT) moves to CExplicit states.
        setCompressionMode(non-EXPLICIT) moves to CNotExplicit states.
        Value-sensitive parameter: mode determines target state.
    end note
